# Stack

## Backend

- **Laravel** — API, routing, Inertia responses
- **Sail** — Docker environment (PHP, PostgreSQL, Node/Vite)
- **PostgreSQL** — Database (per TEXTTOEAT_SPECIFICATION.md)

## Frontend

- **React + Inertia** — SPA-like UX, server-side routing
- **Vite** — Build
- **TailwindCSS** — Styling
- **shadcn/ui** — UI components (Radix primitives, CVA, clsx, tailwind-merge)
- **lucide-react** — Icons

## Conventions

- Run **npm** via Sail: `./vendor/bin/sail npm install`, `./vendor/bin/sail npx ...`
- Use **shadcn/ui** for buttons, dialogs, forms, etc.: `./vendor/bin/sail npx shadcn@latest add button`
- Use **lucide-react** for icons: `import { Plus, Menu } from 'lucide-react'`
- Components live in `resources/js/components/ui/` (shadcn)
